name: Clif Bar Peanut Butter Banana with Dark Chocolate
categories: Peanut Butter Banana with Dark Chocolate
description: Clif took the childhood classic of peanut butter and banana, and brought it to the next level with chunks of rich, dark chocolate. Another tasty new flavour in Clif Bar's line-up of energy options.Ingredients: brown rice syrup, soy protein isolate, peanuts, rolled oats, cane syrup, rice flour, peanut butter, oat fiber, cane sugar, unsweetened chocolate, banana powder, roasted soybeans, soy flour, dried bananas, sea salt, cocoa butter, natural flavors, barley malt extract, soy lecithin, mixed tocopherols (antioxidant).Contains peanuts and soy.May contain tree nuts, milk and wheat.
